Sea buckthorn trees come in many shapes among snowy peaks, streams and lakes, presenting a distinctive spectacle. About 'Journeys in Nature': Western Sichuan series Jiuzhaigou in southwest China's Sichuan Province has been regarded by locals as the "sacred mountain and water." Enjoy the panoramic view of the magnificent fairyland in the five-episode Western Sichuan series. For more Western Sichuan Series | Episode 1: The Iridescent Lake Western Sichuan Series | Episode 2: Calc-sinter Waterfall Western Sichuan Series | Episode 3: Trees in Water (Cover image a screenshot from the video) (If you want to contribute and have specific expertise, please contact us at nature@cgtn.com.)